{"tid":1561201,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"你班on9 人話跳閘你就跳","createTime":"2019-09-11T13:44:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T16:21:18.000Z","uid":147785,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4b6b38c79b7a217ce17a0c582cb72e12427e8f0d","tid":1561201,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:44:48.000Z","msg":"你班友跳之前有冇諗成個流程架?<br />\n<br />\n講咗幾撚多次 比藍屍周到既話係<span style=\"color: red;\">即跑走</span>呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好似果個四眼學生妹咁 電死人之後跑走<br />\n<br />\n隔離個post仲係到吹奏個靚仔哥哥好高EQ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你都唔係叫你高EQ 係叫你跑走無視呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該每次入閘/出閘之前 諗定最壞打算好唔好?<br />\n<br />\n比藍屍/職員周到 跑走就ok 唔好慢慢行 比機會D藍屍對手足郁手郁腳<br />\n<br />\n因為佢地就係想激嬲我地還手 比佢地報警 蝕底係我地手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且比D藍屍影大頭你地就驚? 首先D藍屍次次都係手足跳完先拎部電話出黎影<br />\n<br />\n根本無影到你跳果一刻 佢要再配合港鐵CCTV 先有足夠證據證明你有跳ok?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">加上你戴晒口罩 唔通popo為咗你果$500 特登又拎CCTV 又對番時間 又用人臉識別去搵你出黎咩屌</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以只要唔係比便衣警即時捉到 一律都唔需要理會<br />\n<br />\n比便衣警捉到就唯有配合交罰款 無謂比佢入我地D咩罪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你班友跳之前瞭解下成個應對流程先好唔好?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc1c554ed94b3da1582518688ae70ccf473b585","tid":1561201,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:46:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"19783c9384d521fbc2e393d00d91c5eb0fb08004","tid":1561201,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:48:31.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"33831e3a2740a5e486850bdd128ee7cd10c0f0d2","tid":1561201,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:53:57.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"c126946d09abdef0172cd843224501f568f911ee","tid":1561201,"uid":46309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:21:18.000Z","msg":"今日在大圍想跳，離遠見到有條木嘴望實度閘，心諗仲唔係狗？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zJvhu9k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzJvhu9k.jpg&h=d427fd5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁好啦，算我當黑，我去第邊跳。<br />\n<br />\n去第個出口跳完返去望下佢，<br />\n鴉...... <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢仲啤鳩返我.... <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔撚撚你都對唔住自己啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LcSDeBA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLcSDeBA.png&h=ffbfa8dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cXXEiYewaEo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcXXEiYewaEo&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okQbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=75f05e98\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cXXEiYewaEo</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n█ █ █ █有冇跳閘都入黎聽我講兩句，唔該<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547201</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n████ 明明港鐵係公共服務，點解唔正面表態，而去坐巴士？港豬們想逃避到幾時？？？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRkOwS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRkOwS</a>"}]}